  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201410/f60ca38bfb2b48e299d6d71fa1de3cb1.jpg\" style=\"height: 287px; width: 460px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英乐天天唱》是一档模仿唱歌类节目，目的在于提升大家的英语口语能力。主持人会在每期节目中选取好听的歌曲片段，并给出发音提示和模仿示例。喜欢听音乐的童鞋可要积极参与哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15093/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://media.hiponline.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/sarah-mclachlan.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tSarah McLachlan</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">莎拉-克劳克兰，1968出生于加拿大。她在学生时期曾经学过钢琴、吉他。与此同时，她在学业上也非常努力，Sarah Mclachlan曾进入Nova Scotia学院攻读艺术与设计。由于其天生对于音乐的天赋以及对于音乐的热爱，Sarah Mclachlan在1988年推出她的首张个人专辑Touch，首支单曲Vox得到极大的回响，除了在排行上取得优秀的成绩外，更连续蝉连数周加拿大之声点播冠军曲，而其也突破金唱片的销售量。在这张专辑中，所有的词曲创作都由Sarah McLachlan所包办。Sarah McLachlan空灵清新的唱腔与融合了流行与摇滚的编曲都令人耳目一新，其相当飘渺的歌声却流露出极为成熟的一面。被誉为西洋歌坛&ldquo;知性女声掌门人&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p725703\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tSpend all your time waiting for that second chance<br />\n\tFor the break that will make it OK<br />\n\tThere&lsquo;s always some reason to feel not good enough<br />\n\tAnd it's hard at the end of the day<br />\n\tI need some distraction or a beautiful release<br />\n\tMemories seep from my veins<br />\n\tLet me be empty or weightless and maybe<br />\n\tl'll find some peace tonight</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n\tIn the arms of the angel far away from here<br />\n\tFrom this dark cold hotel room and the endlessness that you feel<br />\n\tYou are pulled from the wreckage of your silent reverie<br />\n\tYou are in the arms of the angel, may you find some comfort here</p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n\tSo tired of the straight line and everywhere you turn<br />\n\tThere's vultures and thieves at your back<br />\n\tThe storm keeps on twisting, you keep on building the lies<br />\n\tThat make up for all that you lack<br />\n\tIt don't make no difference, escape one last time<br />\n\tIt's easier to believe<br />\n\tIn this sweet madness oh this glorious sadness<br />\n\tThat brings me to my knees<br />\n\tIn the arms of the angel far away from here<br />\n\tFrom this dark, cold hotel room and the endlessness that you feel<br />\n\tYou are pulled from the wreckage of your silent reverie<br />\n\tIn the arms of the angel ,may you find some comfort here<br />\n\tIn the arms of the angel, may you find some comfort here</p>\n<p>\n\t讲解：<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p725703\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t模唱：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p725703\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到主持人专业的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15093/item/927691/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p725703/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p725703\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727737/\">百度搜索退出日本揭秘 最大对手并非谷歌</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727862/\">习近平巴基斯坦发表署名文章（双语）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727752/\">记品牌学英文：Durex杜蕾斯这个词咋来的？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727874/\">8张图告诉你 各国古代美女如何化妆</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727554/\">Quora精选：何时的你最心痛？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727864/\">朋友对你的影响到底有多大？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p725457/\">国外知乎：生活中哪些真相让你心碎？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727896/\">你是哪种动物？谷歌玩测试庆祝世界地球日</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727833/\">惊呆！我擦 原来腐国俚语这么有格调！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727568/\">清晨的21句正能量自我暗示</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
