  "description": "<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/entry/201305/6faedd21-129a-4538-8304-05f664711899.jpg\" style=\"height: 400px; width: 400px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p725679\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tSo Baroque music's very much the centre of your work with the group. Why <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/particularly\" target=\"_blank\">particularly</a>? Why you've got this kind of passion for this period?</p>\n<p>\n\tI've always loved Baroque music in studying at the Royal Academy of Music. I was a modern <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/flute\" target=\"_blank\">flute</a> player and discovered Baroque flutes very later on in my studies and that just made sense of the music. The reason Bach wrote the flute sonatas in a particular way was not for the modern flute but for the Baroque flute with its different colours as nuance. The whole thing fits together like a hand in a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/glove\" target=\"_blank\">glove</a>.</p>\n<p>\n\tWell let's hear the group nine, one of its larger <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/manifestation\" target=\"_blank\">manifestations</a> performing part of a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/concerto\" target=\"_blank\">concerto</a> by Vivaldi. Now this one's for piccolo cello, but before we hear it, can you explain what a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/piccolo\" target=\"_blank\">piccolo</a> <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/cello\" target=\"_blank\">cello</a> is?</p>\n<p>\n\tYes. A piccolo cello is a cello with five strings. It's slightly smaller than a normal Baroque cello, maybe 7/8 of the size. And the fifth string is a top string tuned in E whereas a normal cello the top string is tuned in A. And it lends itself to have more tenor like sound when you hear the instrument. And in fact, Bach wrote his Sixth Cello Suite for this piccolo cello and then incorporated a number of arias as an <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/obbligato\" target=\"_blank\">obbligato</a> instrument accompanying mainly the male voice either the tenor or bass.</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(128,128,128); line-height: 25px;\">声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a class=\"creatLinks\" href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/tag/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-family: verdana, arial; border-bottom: rgb(0,90,148) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,90,148); line-height: 25px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"更多英语内容\">英语</a><span style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(128,128,128); line-height: 25px;\">&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p725679/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p725679\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727737/\">百度搜索退出日本揭秘 最大对手并非谷歌</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727862/\">习近平巴基斯坦发表署名文章（双语）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727752/\">记品牌学英文：Durex杜蕾斯这个词咋来的？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727874/\">8张图告诉你 各国古代美女如何化妆</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727554/\">Quora精选：何时的你最心痛？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727864/\">朋友对你的影响到底有多大？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 